item.title: CVE-2020-4066|2024-08-04T07:52:20.926Z -- erelsgl -- limdu
item.description: In Limdu before 0.95, the trainBatch function has a command injection vulnerability. Clients of the Limdu library are unlikely to be aware of this, so they might unwittingly write code that contains a vulnerability. This has been patched in 0.95.
